This paper deals with the satisfiability problem in description logic, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (AI) and logic (LO). It also involves database (DB) and computational complexity (CC) aspects. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.AI and cs.LO. Additionally, since the paper discusses the complexity of the satisfiability problem, it may also belong to cs.CC. Finally, since the paper deals with fragments of ALC, which is a popular description logic, it may also belong to cs.DB and cs.DL.
